// Purpose:    The constitutional laws that no manifold, no substrate, no
//             operation can violate. These are self-evident truths — axioms
//             that are not proven but from which all proofs derive.
//
// Catuskoti State: TRUE | "The laws exist before the system.
//                         They cannot be changed because they were never
//                         'set' — they were discovered."
